## Font Management
### Custom Font: Petrov Sans-Trial
- **Location**: [frontend/src/assets/fonts/Petrov Sans-Trial/](mdc:frontend/src/assets/fonts/Petrov Sans-Trial)
- **CSS File**: [petrov-sans-trial.css](mdc:frontend/src/assets/fonts/Petrov Sans-Trial/petrov-sans-trial.css)
- **Formats**: WOFF2 (preferred) and WOFF (fallback)
- **Weights Available**: Thin (100) to Black (900)

### Font Loading Strategy
```css
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Petrov Sans-Trial';
  src: url('PetrovSans-Trial-Regular.woff2') format('woff2'),
       url('PetrovSans-Trial-Regular.woff') format('woff');
  font-weight: normal;
  font-style: normal;
  font-display: swap; /* Optimize loading performance */
}
```

